casebody.data:
Mary WIEGAND, Personal Representative of the Estate of Keith Wiegand, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Hiroshi YAMASAKI, M.D., Eastside Cardiovascular Medicine, PC, Kishan K. Jasti, M.D., and Osama N. Nunu, M.D., Defendants,
and
St. John Hospital and Medical Center, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157430
COA: 334598 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 4, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's September 28, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
